<div class="container-lg">
  <article class="show-page">
    <section class="show-page-header card">
      <div class="show-page-header-bg"
      ></div>
      <div class="show-page-header-body card justify-content-start">
        <div class="show-page-header-content card-body">
          <div class="show-page-avatar">
            <%= @team.avatar_tag(94) %>
          </div>
          <a href="#" class="show-page-meta badge badge-pill mx-auto">
            <%= svg_icon_tag :site_web %>&nbsp;Site web
          </a>
          <div class="show-page-main-info">
            <h1 class="show-page-title card-title">
              <%= @team.full_name %>
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-0 mb-3"><%= @team.short_name %></p>
            <div class="list-x mb-1">
              <%= @team.badges %>
            </div>
            <small class="text-secondary">Créée le <%= l @team.created_at.to_date, format: :default %></small>
          </div>
          <div class="show-page-side">

          </div>
          <div class="show-page-socials bg-layout bg-md-layout-dark">
        
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <nav class="show-page-nav section-nav players d-lg-none">
      <div class="section-nav-wrapper">
        <scrollactive
          ref="scrollactive"
          :active-class="'active'"
          :offset="116"
        >
          <div class="section-nav-bg shadow-lg">
          <%= link_to team_path(@team, anchor: 'description'), class: "section-nav-link scrollactive-item" do %>
              <%= svg_icon_tag :joueur %>
              <span>Description</span>
            <% end %>
            <%= link_to team_path(@team, anchor: 'recrutement'), class: "section-nav-link scrollactive-item" do %>
              <%= svg_icon_tag :groupe %>
              <span>Recrutement</span>
            <% end %>
            <%= link_to team_path(@team, anchor: 'statistiques'), class: "section-nav-link scrollactive-item" do %>
              <%= svg_icon_tag :groupe %>
              <span>Statistiques</span>
            <% end %>
            <%= link_to team_path(@team, anchor: 'joueurs'), class: "section-nav-link scrollactive-item" do %>
              <%= svg_icon_tag :groupe %>
              <span>Joueurs</span>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </scrollactive>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <section class="show-page-body card">
      <div class="show-page-content card-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-6 list-y">
            <section id="description" class="show-page-section">
              <div class="show-page-section-title">
                <h2>Description</h2>
                <span class="show-page-section-title-separator"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="show-page-section-content">
                <see-more>
                  <p> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Repellat laboriosam eligendi alias quo totam autem consequatur quisquam numquam omnis voluptas! Amet quod dolores doloremque expedita totam, molestias magni consequuntur iste. Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dicta laboriosam non tenetur fugit est numquam eos accusantium cum nesciunt ut veritatis optio quam, illo totam laborum neque odio doloremque quis.</p>
                  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quam ad, inventore dicta accusamus obcaecati suscipit, libero velit doloremque eius a necessitatibus aperiam ducimus, consectetur cupiditate laboriosam id. Est, labore quasi.</p>
                </see-more>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section id="recrutement" class="show-page-section">
              <div class="show-page-section-title">
                <h2>Recrutement</h2>
                <span class="show-page-section-title-separator"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="show-page-section-content">
                <see-more>
                  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Repellat laboriosam eligendi alias quo totam autem consequatur <em>quisquam</em> numquam omnis voluptas! Amet quod dolores doloremque expedita totam, molestias magni consequuntur iste. Lorem ipsum dolor sit, <strong>amet consectetur</strong> adipisicing elit. Dicta laboriosam non tenetur fugit est numquam eos accusantium cum nesciunt ut veritatis optio quam, illo totam laborum neque odio doloremque quis.</p>
                  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quam ad, inventore dicta accusamus obcaecati suscipit, libero velit doloremque eius a necessitatibus aperiam ducimus, consectetur cupiditate laboriosam id. Est, labore quasi.</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Règle 1</li>
                    <li>Règle 2</li>
                    <li>Règle 3</li>
                    <li>Règle 4</li>
                    <li>Règle 5</li>
                  </ul>
                </see-more>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <section id="statistiques" class="show-page-section">
              <div class="show-page-section-title">
                <h2>Statistiques</h2>
                <span class="show-page-section-title-separator"></span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="show-page-section-subtitle h6 d-none d-md-inline-block px-2 py-1 bg-layout rounded-pill"><%= svg_icon_tag(:online) %>&nbsp;Online</h3>
              <div class="show-page-section-body show-page-section-body--with-bg">
                <div class="list-x list-x--lg">
                  <section class="list-y justify-content-center text-center" style="flex: 0 0 33%">
                     <div class="card card-box card-box--sm card-box--square card-box--stat flex-grow-1 mx-1">
                        <h3 class="sr-only">Meilleurs badges</h2>
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <div class="card-content">
                            <% if @team.players&.first&.decorate&.best_rewards_badges(is_online: true, class: 'card-box-icon')&.first %>
                              <%== @team.players&.first&.decorate&.best_rewards_badges(is_online: true, class: 'card-box-icon')&.first %>
                              <button type="button"
                                      class="btn btn-dark btn-sm rounded-pill"
                                      data-toggle="modal"
                                      data-target="#">
                                Voir tout
                              </button>
                              <button class="btn btn-sm btn-see-more btn-see-more--horizontal" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#">
                                <span class="sr-only">Voir plus</span>
                                <%= svg_icon_tag(:suspension) %>
                              </button>
                            <% else %>
                              <small class="my-auto">Aucun badge obtenu</small>
                            <% end %>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="card card-box card-box--sm card-box--square card-box--stat flex-grow-1 mx-1">
                        <h3 class="sr-only">Fragments d'étoiles</h3>
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <div class="card-content">
                            <%= @team.players&.first&.decorate&.points_count(44, is_online: true, class: 'card-box-icon') %>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                  </section>

                  <section class="flex-grow-1">
                    <h3 class="fs-sm mb-3 text-center">Fragment par années</h3>
                    <ul class="list-y list-unstyled text-center mb-0">
                      <% TrackRecord.points_years.sort.reverse.each do |year| %>
                        <li class="list-row list-row--3">
                          <span class="list-row-col flex-grow-1"><%= year %></span>
                          <span>&nbsp;•&nbsp;</span>
                          <span class="list-row-col flex-grow-1"><%=
                            @team.players&.first&.decorate&.points_count(16, year: year, is_online: true, class: 'card-box-icon', delimiter: '&nbsp;')
                          %></span>
                        </li>
                      <% end %>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="text-center mt-3">
                      <button type="button"
                              class="btn btn-sm bg-layout rounded-pill"
                              data-toggle="modal"
                              data-target="#">
                        Voir plus
                      </button>
                    </div>
                  </section>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="show-page-section-subtitle h6 d-none d-md-inline-block px-2 py-1 bg-layout rounded-pill mt-3"><%= svg_icon_tag(:offline) %>&nbsp;Offline</h3>
              <div class="show-page-section-body show-page-section-body--with-bg">
                <div class="list-x list-x--lg">
                  <section class="list-y justify-content-center text-center" style="flex: 0 0 33%">
                     <div class="card card-box card-box--sm card-box--square card-box--stat flex-grow-1 mx-1">
                        <h3 class="sr-only">Meilleurs badges</h2>
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <div class="card-content">
                            <% if @team.players&.first&.decorate&.best_rewards_badges(is_online: false, class: 'card-box-icon')&.first %>
                              <%== @team.players&.first&.decorate&.best_rewards_badges(is_online: false, class: 'card-box-icon')&.first %>
                              <button type="button"
                                      class="btn btn-dark btn-sm rounded-pill"
                                      data-toggle="modal"
                                      data-target="#">
                                Voir tout
                              </button>
                              <button class="btn btn-sm btn-see-more btn-see-more--horizontal" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#">
                                <span class="sr-only">Voir plus</span>
                                <%= svg_icon_tag(:suspension) %>
                              </button>
                            <% else %>
                              <small class="my-auto">Aucun badge obtenu</small>
                            <% end %>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="card card-box card-box--sm card-box--square card-box--stat flex-grow-1 mx-1">
                        <h3 class="sr-only">Fragments d'étoiles</h3>
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <div class="card-content">
                            <%= @team.players&.first&.decorate&.points_count(44, is_online: false, class: 'card-box-icon') %>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                  </section>

                  <section class="flex-grow-1">
                    <h3 class="fs-sm mb-3 text-center">Fragments par années</h3>
                    <ul class="list-y list-unstyled text-center mb-0">
                      <% TrackRecord.points_years.sort.reverse.each do |year| %>
                        <li class="list-row list-row--3">
                          <span class="list-row-col flex-grow-1"><%= year %></span>
                          <span>&nbsp;•&nbsp;</span>
                          <span class="list-row-col flex-grow-1"><%=
                            @team.players&.first&.decorate&.points_count(16, year: year, is_online: false, class: 'card-box-icon', delimiter: '&nbsp;')
                          %></span>
                        </li>
                      <% end %>
                    </ul>
                  </section>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-2">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <section id="joueurs" class="show-page-section">
              <div class="show-page-section-title">
                <h2>Joueurs</h2>
                <span class="show-page-section-title-separator"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="show-page-section-content">
                <div class="mb-3 list-x align-items-center"><small class="mr-3"><%= @team.players.count %> joueur(s)</small><button type="button" class="btn badge badge-with-icon badge-primary py-1 px-2 border-0" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#roster-modal">Voir le roster</button></div>
                <div class="grid">
                  <% @team.players&.each do |player| %>
                    <%= render 'players/player_v2',
                              player: player.decorate,
                              with_addresses: defined?(with_addresses) && with_addresses,
                              with_communities: defined?(with_communities) && with_communities %>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</div>
<%= render 'teams/roster_modal' %>